OL,5, Fourteen beehives and thousands of bees
OL,6, have been stolen.                      
OL,8,FNorth Wales Police believe they were   
OL,9,Fprobably taken at night by someone with
OL,10,Fknowledge of beekeeping from Mynydd y  
OL,11,FGarth, near Llangollen, Denbighshire.  
OL,13,FThe number of bees taken has not been  
OL,14,Fdisclosed, but officers are appealing  
OL,15,Ffor information about anyone with a    
OL,16,F"sudden influx" of hives, or who is    
OL,17,Fselling them or colonies.              
OL,19,FOne experienced beekeeper said it would
OL,20,Fbe a "terrible blow" for the owner.    
